messageBody:
I voted "Don't use" in the usage poll, and that I've been using QS
"3-5 years" in the longevity poll.

It's been 5 years since I discovered QS and created the Jerome font,
but technically speaking, I don't really use it. On the other hand,
QS was an ingredient which went into the development of my personal
shorthand, which I use for journaling, jotting down poems, and things
like that.

Jon
